\\\`\\\`\\\`

This will create a new workspace within the \${workspaceName} directory.

Then, install the plugin package to ensure generators are available:

\\\`\\\`\\\`bash
\${buildInstallCommand(packageManager, getPackageName())}
\\\`\\\`\\\`.
